# Public API Usage

- Do not implement custom backend APIs for this project.
- Use only public APIs for data, such as:
  - https://hp-api.onrender.com/ (Harry Potter API)
  - https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/ (Fake REST API)
  - https://wttr.in (Weather API)
- Prefer using these APIs for all data needs in feature demos and tests. 